import { useEffect } from "react" import { useState } from "react" import { fetchAllStudentWorksheets, putStudentWorksheetInDatabase } from './services/worksheetServices' import { fetchGrades } from './services/gradeServices' import { fetchSubjects } from './services/subjectServices' import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom" export const StudentWorksheets = ({ user }) => { const [grades, setGrades] = useState([]) const [studentWorksheets, setStudentWorksheets] = useState([]) const [subjects, setSubjects] = useState([]) const navigate = useNavigate() const handlEditButton = (studentWorksheet) => { navigate(`edit/${studentWorksheet?.id}`) } const handleStudentWorksheetFetch = () => { fetchAllStudentWorksheets().then((data) => { const filteredData = data.filter((datum) => datum.studentId === user.studentId) setStudentWorksheets(filteredData) }) fetchGrades().then((data) => { setGrades(data) }) fetchSubjects().then((data) => { setSubjects(data) }) } const markWorksheetAsCompleted = (event, studentWorksheet) => { event.preventDefault() const copy = { ...studentWorksheet, isComplete: true } delete copy.worksheet delete copy.student putStudentWorksheetInDatabase(copy).then() } useEffect(() => { handleStudentWorksheetFetch() }, [user.id]) return ( <> {studentWorksheets.map((studentWorksheet) => { return (
